pd_1_com_1text: Do you remember how good times we had?
pd_1_com_2text: Should I grow a full beard?
pd_1_com_3text: Do you want to play Meoan?
pd_7_com_0text: What did you do before you came here?
pd_7_com_1text: Were you a gang? How many you were? And who are they?
pd_7_com_2text: Do you remember to kill a couple; twelve years ago; two days south walking from here?
pd_8_com_0text: Do you mean when we were the best criminals of the whole region?
pd_9_com_0text: What happened to your memory? Did you forgot the other two?
pd_10_com_0text: That couple from the house in the woods? Yeah, why?
pd_11_com_0text: Yes I forgot. Who are they?
pd_12_com_0text: Nasty Lance and Mongrel. You should take some rest, you don't look good.
pd_14_com_0text: Of course not I don't have a clue where they are, I thought you knew!
pd_15_com_0text: Alright, that's all. Take your bottle.
